	* cmdloop.el (read-char): Don't inhibit quit.
	(read-char-exclusive): Ditto.
	(read-char): Signal quit if quit-char was pressed.
	(read-char-exclusive): Ditto.
	(read-quoted-char): Return a character, not integer.

