	Suggested by Karl M. Hegbloom <karlheg@inetarena.com>.
	(describe-key-briefly): Use `princ' "%s" to print object.
	(with-displaying-help-buffer): Kill buffer if it exists, again.
	(describe-key): Use `princ' "%s" to print object.
